<td>8.10</td>
<td>2.75</td>
</tr></tbody></table><h2 id="table3">Table 3: DVA rates from 3 October 1991</h2>
<p>If a rate does not appear in this date range, the most recent earlier rate applies. These rates are indexed each September. This table shows the rates in dollars per fortnight (pf).</p>
<table><thead><tr><th scope="col">VEA Section 27(1)(amputees) Item</th>
<th scope="col">Rate</th>
</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>7</td>
<td>116.30</td>
</tr><tr><td>8</td>
<td>78.50</td>
</tr><tr><td>9</td>
<td>67.40</td>
</tr><tr><td>10</td>
<td>67.40</td>
</tr><tr><td>11</td>
<td>33.70</td>
</tr><tr><td>12</td>
<td>17.70</td>
</tr><tr><td>13</td>
<td>33.70</td>
</tr><tr><td>14</td>
<td>17.70</td>
</tr><tr><td>15</td>
<td>26.10</td>
</tr></tbody></table><h3>Notes for Table 1</h3>
<p>Service Pensions are the same rate as <a href="../guide-social-security-law/acronyms#age" title="Age pension">Age</a> Pensions.</p>
<table><thead><tr><th scope="col">
<p>Notes</p>
</th>
<th scope="col">
<p>Explanation</p>
</th>
</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td id="A">A</td>
<td>These rates are indexed each March and September.</td>
</tr><tr><td id="B">B</td>
<td>These rates are indexed each September.</td>
</tr><tr><td id="C">C</td>
<td>
<p>EDA payment was introduced on 1 December 1988. It is payable to extremely disabled veterans who:</p>
<ul><li>are receiving 100% Disability Pension,</li>
<li>have reached retiring age,</li>
<li>are not receiving an Intermediate or Special Rate Pension, and</li>
<li>satisfy medical criteria.</li>
</ul><p>The EDA is payable at 50% of the general rate and is treated as income for social security purposes.</p>
</td>
</tr><tr><td id="D">D</td>
<td>From 1 November 1986, Social Security Pension is payable subject to a ceiling of $120.10 a fortnight to recipients of WWP.</td>
</tr><tr><td id="E">E</td>
<td>These rates are indexed each January.</td>
</tr><tr><td id="F">F</td>
<td>Domestic allowance is now absorbed into the basic pension, but still shown separately by DVA.</td>
</tr></tbody></table><div class="reference">
<p><strong>Act reference:</strong> <a href="https://www.legislation.gov.au/Series/C2004A04121" title="Social Security Act 1991">SSAct</a> section 8(1)-'income', section 23(1)-'service pension', section 23(1)-'social security pension'</p>
